<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Для тебя 🌿</title>

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #b8f5c4 0%, #5fbd75 45%, #2f7d46 100%);
    }

    .scene {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .sunlight {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 10%, rgba(255,255,255,0.55), transparent 45%);
      animation: glow 5s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
    }

    @keyframes glow {
      from { opacity: 0.55; }
      to { opacity: 0.9; }
    }

    .bird {
      position: absolute;
      font-size: 28px;
      animation: fly 14s linear infinite;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .bird.one { top: 14%; left: -10%; animation-delay: 0s; }
    .bird.two { top: 24%; left: -20%; animation-delay: 4s; font-size: 22px; }
    .bird.three { top: 18%; left: -30%; animation-delay: 8s; font-size: 20px; }

    @keyframes fly {
      from { transform: translateX(0) translateY(0); }
      to { transform: translateX(130vw) translateY(-30px); }
    }

    .vines {
      position: absolute;
      top: -10px;
      width: 100%;
      height: 150px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, #2f8f4e 0 12px, transparent 13px),
        radial-gradient(circle at 25% 35%, #1d7438 0 10px, transparent 11px),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 20%, #2f8f4e 0 14px, transparent 15px),
        radial-gradient(circle at 75% 30%, #1d7438 0 12px, transparent 13px),
        radial-gradient(circle at 90% 15%, #2f8f4e 0 10px, transparent 11px);
      animation: vinesMove 4s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
    }

    @keyframes vinesMove {
      from { transform: translateY(0); }
      to { transform: translateY(8px); }
    }

    .grass {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 170px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #3fa85c, #1f6f39);
      border-radius: 55% 55% 0 0;
      animation: grassMove 3s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
    }

    @keyframes grassMove {
      from { transform: scaleX(1); }
      to { transform: scaleX(1.03); }
    }

    .bush {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 70px;
      width: 180px;
      height: 100px;
      background: #23783d;
      border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow:
        45px -20px 0 #2f9b50,
        90px 5px 0 #1f6f39;
      animation: bushMove 4s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
    }

    .bush.left { left: -40px; }
    .bush.right { right: 40px; transform: scaleX(-1); }

    @keyframes bushMove {
      from { filter: brightness(1); }
      to { filter: brightness(1.12); }
    }

    .card {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 420px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      top: 36%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      padding: 34px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(20, 80, 35, 0.35);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    }

    h1 {
      color: #1f6f39;
      font-size: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    p {
      color: #315c3b;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }

    button {
      border: none;
      padding: 15px 28px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38b86a, #1f7f43);
      color: white;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(31, 127, 67, 0.45);
      transition: 0.25s;
    }

    button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.03);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(31, 127, 67, 0.55);
    }

    .leaf {
      position: absolute;
      top: -40px;
      font-size: 24px;
      animation: fall 8s linear infinite;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .leaf:nth-child(1) { left: 15%; animation-delay: 0s; }
    .leaf:nth-child(2) { left: 45%; animation-delay: 2s; }
    .leaf:nth-child(3) { left: 75%; animation-delay: 4s; }

    @keyframes fall {
      0% { transform: translateY(-40px) rotate(0deg); }
      100% { transform: translateY(110vh) rotate(260deg); }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="scene">
    <div class="sunlight"></div>

    <div class="vines"></div>

    <div class="bird one">🕊️</div>
    <div class="bird two">🐦</div>
    <div class="bird three">🕊️</div>

    <div class="leaf">🍃</div>
    <div class="leaf">🌿</div>
    <div class="leaf">🍃</div>

    <div class="card">
      <h1>Привет 💚</h1>
      <p>
        У меня есть для тебя маленький необычный сюрприз.
        Нажми на кнопку, чтобы продолжить 🌿
      </p>

      <button onclick="nextPage()">Нажми, чтобы продолжить</button>
    </div>

    <div class="bush left"></div>
    <div class="bush right"></div>
    <div class="grass"></div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function nextPage() {
      alert("Тут будет вторая страница 💚");
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
